Package: earthui
Title: Interactive GUI for Enhanced Adaptive Regression Through Hinges
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("William", "Craytor", , "bcraytor@proton.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: William Craytor [aut, cre]
Maintainer: William Craytor <bcraytor@proton.me>
Description: Provides a Shiny-based graphical user interface for the 'earth'
    package, enabling interactive building and exploration of multivariate
    adaptive regression spline models. Features include data import from CSV
    and Excel files, automatic detection of categorical variables, interactive
    control of interaction terms via an allowed matrix, comprehensive model
    diagnostics with variable importance and partial dependence plots, and
    publication-quality report generation via 'Quarto'.
License: AGPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/wcraytor/earthui
BugReports: https://github.com/wcraytor/earthui/issues
